    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out as not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II centrifugal blood pump in the CPB setting, as described in the Claim and Requirement nodes. No unresolved deficiencies were identified. Decision: Accepted.",
